Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:06.40,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,And it's been really dry lately, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:09.78,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,So Yumiko brought this little \Nhumidifier to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:12.65,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,and it was spitting out a ton \Nof steam all through class!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:18.53,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You know, those new ones powered \Nby... USJ? USA? That kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.42,0:00:17.78,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That slight smile hasn't \Nchanged since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:20.96,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Our days haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:21.45,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to have one of those in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.20,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Right, Hikki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:24.54,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Days spent just trying not to run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:25.84,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Earth to Hikki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:30.30,Ore_Main,Hikki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm listening. And it's USB.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:33.36,Ore_Main,Hikki,0000,0000,0000,,Why should humidifiers have to \Nget their power from America?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:35.24,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it! USB!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:39.22,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Cell phones these days can be \Ncharged with that USB thing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.36,0:00:43.73,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what should we do for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:47.23,Ore_Main_Top,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be busy getting ready for the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:47.23,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,To keep from making the things \Nwe've lost into excuses,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:48.19,Ore_Main_Top,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.65,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,we steel ourselves more than usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:53.78,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,trying harder than usual \Nto act the same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:57.41,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas, huh? I know about Ebina, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:00:59.16,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,What about you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:01.26,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to pass, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:03.38,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.67,0:01:05.85,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,You have plans or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:07.92,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:10.33,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Hikki...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:16.27,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking at us too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.06,Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(235,1)}My Teen\NRomantic\NComedy\N{\c&H8D39E0&}SNAFU\N{\c&HDCA02E&}TOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:50.85,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Er, I wasn't really looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.34,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,No, you were totally looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:55.15,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I was kinda freaked out, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.58,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who should \Nstop looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.39,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Oh, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:01.53,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I just sensed something, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.90,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Some kind of pressure, or chill...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:05.65,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Those two don't feel anything alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:06.91,Ore_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.25,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.02,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:13.13,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,you guys were drawing \Nattention to yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.85,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Just then, somewhere inside, \Nsomething hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:21.09,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I watching them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.26,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.03,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Sai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:26.07,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.67,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:32.60,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought it was unusual to see \Nyou two talking in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.06,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.52,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.03,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.46,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we were kind of talking \Nabout club stuff, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.03,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, your club, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:46.79,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you guys are back to doing \Nclub work like before, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:48.28,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:52.58,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, you can come to us \Nif you ever need help again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.46,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:58.00,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You can come, even if you \Ndon't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:00.22,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:01.92,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You're motivated for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.02,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.40,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Hikki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:13.06,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to club together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.19,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.18,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:45.90,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you leave first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:47.91,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't. I'm waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:49.18,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:52.18,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so you don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:54.59,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.18,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what do you do at lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:07.91,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh... Same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.70,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.32,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.12,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:18.80,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:30.47,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yahello, Yukinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:40.92,Ore_Main_Top,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,And he said it's unusual for me and \NHikki to talk in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.80,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,How long will this continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.86,Ore_Main_Top,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Did he? I suppose it might be unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.62,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,How long will we be able to keep this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.00,Ore_Main_Top,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. Right, Hikki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:49.22,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen when we \Ncan't keep it up anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:48.22,Ore_Main_Top,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, that was probably the first \Ntime we talked that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:50.39,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It kinda tired me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.24,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It tired you out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:54.18,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I was probably watching \NHayama and his buddies
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:56.14,Ore_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,because I felt like they'd teach me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:59.54,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,how to mend something that's fallen apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:02.64,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.96,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.63,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:08.69,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in trouble! I'm in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:11.18,Ore_Main,Troha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in serious trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:13.99,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,A Christmas event?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:14.89,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:17.94,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So that's your first student council job...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:21.44,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,It's a joint thing with \NKaihin General High School,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:25.82,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,and I guess we're supposed to entertain \Nold folks and preschool kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:29.22,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Who came up with that idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.12,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,It was the other school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.65,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd ever suggest something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:34.49,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:38.68,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,So of course, I'd normally \Nturn them down, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:41.30,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I have plans for Christmas, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.13,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You'd turn them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.67,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're handling your \Nfreedom too personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.90,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,But Hiratsuka-sensei is telling us to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.34,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I should've known she had a hand in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:55.01,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,So I got started with things, \Nbut it's just not coming together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.91,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it goes when you \Ndeal with other schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:58.12,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:07:01.70,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you should've talked to \NShiromeguri-senpai before coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.86,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... w-well... I mean, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:06.61,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:10.57,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bother her when she's \Nstudying for entrance exams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:14.66,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you just don't like \NMeguri-senpai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:18.21,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only ones I can turn to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:36.33,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... I have an idea of \Nwhat's going on, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:37.95,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.77,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:43.20,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since anyone's \Nasked for our help, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:45.61,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't done anything like this lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:47.65,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,So, just like before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:54.28,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... it couldn't hurt \Nto try... I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:56.76,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.79,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.86,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think we should mess with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.67,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's the student council's problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:10.32,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I don't think it's a good \Nthing to rely on other people right
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:12.09,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,after you take over as president.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:14.68,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:17.33,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,We're not a jack-of-all-trades service.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.31,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,We only help people out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:22.69,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this is your job. Got it? Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:25.89,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I took over as president \Nbecause you said I should!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:27.77,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to do something about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.48,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Being told that weakens me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:33.36,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It only makes sense that I should take \Nresponsibility for Isshiki Iroha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.49,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Which means there's one other person
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:39.35,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to take responsibility for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.83,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Would you object to me helping you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.85,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,on a personal level, not for the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:50.09,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, yeah, I'm fine with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:53.30,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,If it's just you alone, I can use—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:57.99,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I can rest easy. I mean, I can rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:59.03,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to correct yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.34,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What about Hayama, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:04.08,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't times like these when you \Nshould get him to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:10.80,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,This is a tough job, so I didn't \Nwant to bother him with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:13.32,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't mind bothering \Nme? I mean, not that I care...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:17.66,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Still, who knew she'd say something noble \Nlike she didn't want to bother him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.94,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even Isshiki can \Nact like a girl in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:22.10,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta admire that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.23,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, with stuff like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:27.26,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,it's cute how he can't handle simple things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:29.46,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,It's his mistakes that I like about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:33.79,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Asking him to do something that's \Nactually hard would just scare him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:35.49,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:36.71,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Some winning personality she's got.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.86,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back! Return to me my admiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.23,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's meet at the \Nschool gate afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:45.06,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What? We're starting today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:46.81,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:50.27,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then change the meeting location.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:55.13,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be embarrassing if my friends saw \Nus leaving together and started rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:56.66,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:59.58,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, is she in the wrong generation \Nto get the humor of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:03.53,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,She's not even responding with \N"But you don't have any friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:04.88,Ore_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Total poker face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.79,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.62,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,You know where the community center is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:10.77,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.88,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll head there after I get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:15.38,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you there, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:18.63,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You really are sneaky...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.82,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,What did Iroha-chan say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:26.90,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,She whined a lot, but she \Nseemed to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:27.89,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:31.70,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,And that was the first time in a while \Nthat I hoped we could do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:34.00,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Something else will come up soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:40.41,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's actually better if \Nwe don't get any requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:43.24,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,If we just don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.37,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.66,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Then what have I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.54,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What have we...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:53.44,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,been doing all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:06.83,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I made you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:08.64,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I had a little shopping to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:11.52,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.97,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What's that irritating face for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:20.15,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't trying to call attention to how \Nheavy your bags are so I'd carry them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:23.09,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no, that was just a natural reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:27.33,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't trying to hit on me, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.14,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. My heart fluttered for a moment, \Nbut after calming down, I still can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:32.58,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:36.21,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to \Nget rejected by this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:40.47,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:43.26,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No big deal. It's part of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.97,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're so dependable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:48.04,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, take care of \Nthe next part, too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.14,Lecture_11:48,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Lecture Room 1
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.93,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.28,comm_center_12:01,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Chiba City Mihama Ward Takasu Community Center
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:07.62,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tamanawa, student council president \Nof Kaihin General High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:08.76,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.41,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.62,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:15.21,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,we had the chance to plan this together, \Nas two fresh, rookie presidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.56,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hoping we can forge a \Npartnership of mutual respect
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:21.50,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,and bring about a synergetic effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:24.13,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,He throws a good punch \Nright from the get-go...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.06,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Iroha-chan, got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:27.01,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:29.49,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hikigaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:33.44,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:36.16,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,You're on the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:36.91,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.48,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Same as me, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:41.74,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here because my friend \Nasked me to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.85,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait, you're alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.84,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,All the time, pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.49,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? That's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:48.49,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:50.24,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:56.79,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, there's someone here you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.59,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The way you said that sounded like
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:02.08,Ore_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Someone exists that you \Nknow?" Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:05.75,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you've seen her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:09.22,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the girl, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:12.38,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she was my classmate in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.39,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:17.08,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the meeting's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:18.73,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,This way, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:21.23,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'd rather stay on the sidelines...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.24,plan_13:21,Text,0000,0000,0000,,About the Christmas Event Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:25.27,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so just like last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:27.41,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,let's start by brainstorming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:29.87,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,First on the agenda is the event concept
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:32.33,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,and sharing of ideas for activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:41.24,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the demands that fall \Non us as high school students,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:43.28,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we need to come up with some
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.26,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,innovation befitting of young minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:50.88,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, naturally, we need \Nto ponder on the premise of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:53.02,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,a win-win relationship with the community.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:58.53,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll probably have to think \Nstrategically in terms of cost-effectiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.48,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:03.29,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:06.86,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,The other school is making \Nsuggestions for us, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.11,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:11.24,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, isn't there something \Nmore important to consider?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:20.74,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,We should use logical thinking \Nto think logically.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:22.63,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't those the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.76,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,How many times are we supposed to think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:28.31,Ore_Italics,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,We should put ourselves in the customer's \Nplace to see from the customers' perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:30.42,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Again, aren't those the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.26,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do we have \Nto become the customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.54,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then we could give some thought to outsourcing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.77,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,With our current method, that might \Nbe tough to fit in the scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.62,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:40.11,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's a chance it could \Nbe rescheduled, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:42.37,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we give ourselves \Nmore of a buffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:45.03,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's true. We should \Nlook at the whole picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:59.22,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Are you getting an idea of how it all works?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.96,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't understand a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:04.21,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they were saying some \Ndifficult stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:08.08,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,But when I say stuff like "Wow, \NI need to work hard, too,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:09.43,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,that goes over really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:13.74,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, all I really have to do \Nis email back and forth with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:15.44,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get stabbed someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:19.35,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,But you're like that sometimes, too, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:22.85,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Like you're trying to look \Nsmart or interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:24.12,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put me on their level.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:25.94,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about looking interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.35,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:30.24,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:35.54,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I've worked out what we need \Nto do, so let's start tackling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.87,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:42.39,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be getting on \Nwell enough with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:44.78,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:48.67,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one who taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.40,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,that younger girls trying to \Nlearn something are cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:53.59,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't teach you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:56.24,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But now you don't need me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.03,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:03.38,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Iroha-chan, can you take care of these, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:05.51,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Also this, and this, and this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.47,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:11.57,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything you don't \Nunderstand, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:13.40,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain it so you can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:24.75,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,So as you heard, getting the minutes \Ntogether will be our job, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.02,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:33.95,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like we can say the \Nstudent council is functioning well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.97,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there's some \Nreservation between them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.81,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like that's \Nhindering their communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.72,Ore_Main_Top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,President, is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.48,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I'll check.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:45.47,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Also, about the way this \Nwork is progressing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:46.43,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:50.75,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.45,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,He's the vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.41,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've got it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.04,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he likes me much...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:05.32,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,But that's how it always goes at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.94,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,He'll get used to me eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.68,library_17:19,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Mihama\NLibrary
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.68,comm_fest_17:19,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu {\c&H2E282B&}Community {\c&H29243A&}Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:29.02,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.33,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Your reactions are too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:36.24,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're just being sneaky with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:39.85,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. I'm just being natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:52.30,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, I think that's \Npretty sneaky of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:55.67,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. I'm just being natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:58.05,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:02.06,Lecture_11:48,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Lecture Room 1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:02.06,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Our outline of the plan hasn't \Ncompletely solidified yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:04.64,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,so let's continue our \Nbrainstorming from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:07.38,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're doing this, \NI'd like to make it more flashy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:09.02,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:12.15,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We should do something big, \Nsomething with a real bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:19.04,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we may have been pulling \Neverything together too closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:21.12,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really? Something \Nwas "pulled together"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:26.37,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The minutes don't have anything in them \Nbut "logical thinking blah blah blah."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.91,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I'm supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:32.50,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's because nothing \Nspecific has been settled on yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.89,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should increase the scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:35.87,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.22,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:40.19,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:44.85,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have the time or the \Npersonnel to increase the scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.64,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:50.65,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,When brainstorming, you don't \Nreject another's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:54.44,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,"We can't make this any bigger because \Nwe lack the time and personnel."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:56.15,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,"So how should we deal with that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:58.78,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,We expand the discussion in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.28,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't come to a conclusion right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.41,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,So your opinion doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:04.56,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:07.58,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,For all you said, you wasted no \Ntime rejecting my opinion...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:10.22,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Let's discuss how to make it possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:14.64,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we bring in \Nmore local high schools?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:17.09,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa. Why do people \Nwho want to look interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.76,Ore_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,love working with others so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:21.89,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no merit in bringing in more schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:25.65,Ore_Main_Top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good. We'd be \Ninvolving the community.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:28.00,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But a simple objection like \Nthat would be crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:28.00,Ore_Main_Top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we could work \Ntoward closing generation gaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.02,Ore_Main_Top,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That'll work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:32.48,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to say this in a \Nway that fits their rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.65,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a fresh idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.08,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,As a counter to your previous suggestion,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:41.57,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I feel it would be better to strive \Nfor the maximum synergetic effect
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:45.40,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,by having our two schools cooperate \Nto build a closer relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:46.95,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:53.21,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:56.54,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,So it shouldn't be a high school. \NPerhaps college students...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:58.01,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:01.39,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait. Then we can't take initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:04.30,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we're to reach a consensus \Nwith our stakeholders,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:08.65,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,we need a partnership in which we can offer \Nclear suggestions of a solid manifesto...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:10.65,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:13.42,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one saying it, \Nand I don't know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.19,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:16.94,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,He understood that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:20.94,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about a local elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:24.31,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,What do you call it? "Gameducation"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:27.42,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,If we can make the work enjoyable,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:30.38,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,maybe we could get a local \Nelementary school to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.25,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be win-win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.75,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Win-win!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.83,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:36.75,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What's the thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:40.75,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,If we handle the appointment and \Nnegotiation of an elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:44.15,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,If you could handle them after \Nthat, I'd appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:45.76,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.64,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:52.97,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:03.94,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:08.89,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Were you on the student council \Nor anything in middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:10.19,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,You seem used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:11.56,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.04,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Did you break up with your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:16.76,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:20.71,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it just seemed like you \Nhad your sights on Isshiki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:29.60,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have broken up. \NI've never had a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:34.19,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I thought you were going \Nout with one of those two girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:35.41,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Which two girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:37.53,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the ones who \Nshowed up on that date.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:43.53,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,They're just... in the same club as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:46.33,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a club? Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:48.42,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The Service Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.33,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:54.25,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.53,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.36,0:21:58.09,Ore_Main_Top,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what does that club do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:02.68,Ore_Main_Top,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That's my first "seriously" of the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:02.77,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is a club that \Ndoesn't make much sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:05.55,Ore_Main_Top,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of a Service Club before!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:05.55,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:09.55,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Without Incident,\N\N\N\NThe Congress Dances, But Does Not Progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:08.94,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's really nothing to laugh about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:24:08.88,Next_Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,#07 Yet, That Room Continues to Play Out the Endless Days.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:42.86,Ore_Main_Top,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,We should consider the priority of each task
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:44.81,Ore_Main_Top,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,and come up with an order of priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.81,0:23:46.11,Ore_Main_Top,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That'll work!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.81,0:23:46.11,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Those mean the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:47.71,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do you want to prioritize?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.39,0:23:50.64,Ore_Main_Top,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,What's being demanded of us now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.64,0:23:54.33,Ore_Main_Top,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,is the flexibility of flexible ideas \Nthat only young minds can invent!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.33,0:23:55.10,Ore_Main_Top,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That's the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.33,0:23:55.57,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Those mean the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.57,0:23:57.35,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,How flexible are we supposed to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:24:02.18,Ore_Main_Top,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Now our scheme to drop all of \Nour resources into this event is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.18,0:24:04.09,Ore_Main_Top,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to our next brainstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.33,0:24:08.37,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Getting ready is all we've done...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.37,0:24:10.37,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
